ijfhout%2C+S.S.&amp;rft.au=Edwards%2C+T.L.&amp;rft.au=Golledge%2C+N.R.&amp;rft.au=Hemer%2C+M.&amp;rft.au=Kopp%2C+R.E.&amp;rft.au=Krinner%2C+G.&amp;rft.au=Mix%2C+A.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.ch%2Freport%2Far6%2Fwg1%2Fdownloads%2Freport%2FIPCC_AR6_WGI_Chapter09.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHistory+of+climate+change+science" class="Z3988"></span></span>
